commit.message: Implemented the new changes to emmy proposal
Emmy proposal is now fully supported
implemented new emmyPlusDelay on baker function
Started to implement unit tests and changed the notification package
Emmy proposal support at 70% and lint improvements
changed default fee values and improved how incoming bakings are fetched
Added a UI to send transactions and fixed delegate re-activation
Reimplemented how the nonces logic and moved operation functions from rpc
Fixed a concurrency problem on baking controller, now only 1 instance of monitorHeads will be running
Removed Tzcan api to request completed bakings
